        <div class="block text-block">
         <h3 class="block-header">
          Contact
          <span>
           SHOP
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p>
           SHOP is
           <span>
            located in the Student Health Center, across the street from Colleges 9 &amp; 10. As you walk up the ramp to the Health Center, SHOP is located in the building on your left, next to the Pharmacy.
           </span>
          </p>
          <p>
           <span>
            <img alt="" height="100" hspace="NaN" src="images/shop-compass-gray.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="200"/>
           </span>
          </p>
          <p>
